org.cpsolver.exam.reports

Class ExamInstructorConflicts

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.exam.reports.ExamInstructorConflicts

  • public class ExamInstructorConflicts
extends Object
    Export instructor direct, back-to-back, and more than two exams a day conflicts into a CSV file.

    Usage: 
    
     new ExamInstructorConflicts(model).report().save(file);

    Version:
